quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  63,1,"Si naafiqii…ďe …ďeen ngrii e maa, …ďe mbi'a: ""Mi…óen ceedii won'de ko a Nulaa…óo Allah"". Allah no anndi won'de pellet, ko a Nulaa…óo makko; Allah no seedii won'de pellet, naafiqii…ďe …ďeen ko fenoo…ďe."
  63,2,"∆Āe njogitorri goondooje ma…ď…ďe …óeen heedo, …ďe paddii laawol Allah ngol. Pellet, fii ko …ďe ngollaynoo kon bonii!"
  63,3,"∆äuim noon ko tawde …ďe gooŇč…óinii, refti …ďe njeddi, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen notaa e mum; kam…ďe on …ďe paamataa."
  63,4,"Si a yi'ii …ďe, …ďalli ma…ď…ďe welete; si …ďe wowlii, a nana konngu…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin. Hi…ďe mba'i wa pecce …ďaaraa…óe, hi…ďe cikka kala eewnaango ko e hoore ma…ď…ďe. Ko …ďeen tigi ngoni a√Ī…ďe …ďen, reeno…ďe. Allah hu…óii …ďe ! Ko honno …ďe nkiiltiratool (e goonga) !"
  63,5,"Si …ďe mbianaama: ""ngaree Nulaa…óo Allah on imsinanoo on"", …ďe hayla ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óeen, nji'aa hi…ďe …óuurnoo hara ko …ďe townitii…ďe."
  63,6,"Hino fota e ma…ď…ďe, foti a imsinani …ďe maa hara a imsinanaaki …ďe: Allah yaafotaako …ďe fes, pellet, Allah feewnataa yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe …ďeen."
  63,7,"Ko …ďeen ngoni wioo…ďe wote nafqee won…ďe e sera nelaa…ó√† haa …ďe ceerta na woodani Alla moftir…ói kammuuji e leydi kono tan naafiqee…ďe …ďe paamatah."
  63,8,"Ho…ďe mbia si en nduttiima Madiina ma …ďur…ďe teddude njaltin …ďur…ďe hoyde …ďe, woodanii Alla teddungal e nelaa…óo makko e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe, kono tan naafige en nganndah."
  63,9,"Eehey mon gooŇč…óin…ďe woto sokli mon jaw…óeele mon e …ďi…ď…ďe mon gaa e innude Alla kala ba…ó…óo …óuum ko …ďeen ngoni pertu…ďe …ďe."
  63,10,"Nafqe ko Alla arsakini on ko, ko adii nde maayde arata e gooto e mon o wi'a joom am a leelnantaa kam haa e happu …ďadii…óo mi sakkoro mi wona e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďe."
  63,11,"Alla nee…ďnantah hay fittaandu wo'oturu si happu manndu arii Alla na humpatii ko ngolloton ko."
